[
    {
        "text": "We fear the idea of personal change...",
        "startTime": 507,
        "endTime": 3381,
        "slowStartTime": 910,
        "slowEndTime": 5297
    },
    {
        "text": "...because we think that we have to sacrifice something to give something up.",
        "startTime": 4306,
        "endTime": 7565,
        "slowStartTime": 6609,
        "slowEndTime": 11572
    },
    {
        "text": "But human beings, at our best, are so inventive and creative and ingenious.",
        "startTime": 7971,
        "endTime": 13347,
        "slowStartTime": 12107,
        "slowEndTime": 20245
    },
    {
        "text": "And I think that when we use love and compassion as our guiding principles,...",
        "startTime": 13909,
        "endTime": 20669,
        "slowStartTime": 21013,
        "slowEndTime": 31228
    },
    {
        "text": "...we can create, develop and implement systems of change...",
        "startTime": 21310,
        "endTime": 25620,
        "slowStartTime": 32115,
        "slowEndTime": 38655
    },
    {
        "text": "...that are beneficial to all sentient beings and to the environment.",
        "startTime": 25713,
        "endTime": 28733,
        "slowStartTime": 38720,
        "slowEndTime": 43325
    },
    {
        "text": "I've been a scoundrel all my life.",
        "startTime": 29255,
        "endTime": 30832,
        "slowStartTime": 44033,
        "slowEndTime": 46473
    },
    {
        "text": "I have been selfish.",
        "startTime": 31507,
        "endTime": 32656,
        "slowStartTime": 47410,
        "slowEndTime": 49209
    },
    {
        "text": "I've been cruel at times, hard to work with and ungrateful.",
        "startTime": 33091,
        "endTime": 37330,
        "slowStartTime": 49786,
        "slowEndTime": 56220
    },
    {
        "text": "But, so many of you in this room have given me a second chance.",
        "startTime": 37769,
        "endTime": 41915,
        "slowStartTime": 56803,
        "slowEndTime": 63098
    },
    {
        "text": "And I think that's when we're at our best:...",
        "startTime": 42299,
        "endTime": 44564,
        "slowStartTime": 63598,
        "slowEndTime": 67071
    },
    {
        "text": "...when we support each other. Not when we cancel each other out for past mistakes,...",
        "startTime": 45968,
        "endTime": 49737,
        "slowStartTime": 69102,
        "slowEndTime": 74830
    },
    {
        "text": "...but when we help each other to grow, when we educate each other,...",
        "startTime": 50158,
        "endTime": 53133,
        "slowStartTime": 75387,
        "slowEndTime": 79924
    },
    {
        "text": "...when we guide each other towards redemption.",
        "startTime": 53215,
        "endTime": 55191,
        "slowStartTime": 79972,
        "slowEndTime": 83012
    },
    {
        "text": "That is the best of humanity.",
        "startTime": 55710,
        "endTime": 57411,
        "slowStartTime": 83715,
        "slowEndTime": 86342
    },
    {
        "text": "When he was 17, my brother wrote this lyric.",
        "startTime": 57961,
        "endTime": 61807,
        "slowStartTime": 87091,
        "slowEndTime": 92936
    },
    {
        "text": "He said, \"Run to the rescue with love and peace will follow.\"",
        "startTime": 62231,
        "endTime": 66695,
        "slowStartTime": 93496,
        "slowEndTime": 100267
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you.",
        "startTime": 67013,
        "endTime": 67403,
        "slowStartTime": 100670,
        "slowEndTime": 101329
    }
]